window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The return of the famous shared-world superhero books created and edited by George R. R. Martin, author of <i>A Song of Ice and Fire</i>.&nbsp;</p> <p>Perfect for current fans and new listeners alike, <i>Mississippi Roll</i> is an all-new adventurous jaunt along one of America's greatest rivers, featuring many beloved characters from the Wild Cards universe.&nbsp;</p> <p>Edited by number one <i>New York Times</i> best-selling author George R. R. Martin, <i>Mississippi Roll</i> features the writing talents of Stephen Leigh, David D. Levine, John Jos. Miller, Kevin Andrew Murphy, Cherie Priest, and Carrie Vaughn.&nbsp;</p>"; 
